<body>
    <div type="letter"><pb facs="3713805" n="1"/>
        <opener><salute><lb/>Celeberrimo &amp; Excellentissimo Mathematico
            <lb/>JOANNI BERNOULLIO</salute>
            <lb/>Joh. Gesnerus s. pl. d.</opener>
        <p>
            <lb/>Redit ad TE amicissimum Bernoulli egregium D. Rameau
            <lb/>opusculum de Musices principium. gratias habeo pro communicato opere
            <lb/>cujus author &amp; praxi musica per universam Galliam celebratur, &amp; Acade<lb/>mi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scientiarum imprimis placere videtur. Pleniorem Theoriam &amp; Praxin
            <lb/>musicas ante pluros a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>os edidit ex qua multa &amp; utilia hausi, etsi mihi
            <lb/>videatur aliquantum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vero Harmoniae principio discedere, quod in vario
            <lb/>rum consensu consistere videtur; et inde ratio est quod in ratione 1:1 minor
            <lb/>sit pulchritudo quam in 1:2 vel octava &amp; in ea multo minor quam in
            <lb/>ratione 2:3 vel quinta; quando vero quintas, octavas aut consonantias
            <lb/>omnium ordinum sibi substitui posse existimat, me non habet consentien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem, nec in eo quod fundamentum musicas ex <del/>solo principio sit hau<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riendum quod tres diversi Toni in eadem percussa chorda percipiantur: periti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ores enim Musici &amp; qui assuetam habent hiace delicius aures plures
            <lb/>observant. Illustris <hi rend="u">Crameri</hi> Tractatum analyticum de lineis
            <lb/>curvis su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o cum ardore pervolvo &amp; pulcerrima inventa in eo lego, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> magna
            <lb/>evidentia ab ipse pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ponita sunt &amp; a calculo quoque facilitandum s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pe nu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mero multum tribuunt. Optandum esset ut TE interprete &amp; sensore eam
            <lb/>partem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> lineas Transcendentales pertractat c. publico co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicet Cel.
            <lb/>Eulerus qui ideo argumentum pertractavit generaliora fere ubique affert
            <lb/>&amp; pulcherrima, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tamen in Crameriano opere aliquanto magis ad usum acco<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>modata videatur.</p>
<p>D. Sultzerus aegre Basileâ tam cito discedebat.</p>
        <pb facs="3713806" n="2"/>       
        <p><lb/>Qui institutiones analyticas D. Agnese apud nos legant aut nemo est aut
            <lb/>unus, ut non facile invenirem qui latinè interpretaretur. Maclaurini metho<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dus fluxionum gallice prodiit curâ D. Rezenas, qui ejusd. authoris intro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ductionem in algebram <del/>gallice vertit.</p>
        <p><lb/>Equidem sors mihi diu invidet Amicissimum meum Bernoullium
            <lb/>Basilea videndi, sed ego audentios contra ibo nec à proposito desistam eam
            <lb/>primam selecturus occasionem quam sanitas &amp; negotia mea concedent. Et sane
            <lb/><del/><add>nisi</add> haed Temporis ratio qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sanitati est infecta impediisset <del/>ferias
            <lb/>autumnales apud Vos transegissem, data tua mihi quoq<choice><orig><g ref="#ue">uͤ</g></orig><reg>ü</reg></choice> fuisset occasio perlustran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di Thesaurum librorum rerumque naturalium beati D. Stehelini veteris quondam
            <lb/>amici. <del/>Catalogus quem benevole co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicasti parum me in no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ullis leni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deret<!-- unsicheres Wort, RG 11.01.2024 --> cum s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>penumero editionis a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>us locusque desint &amp; tituli erronei adscribantur.
            <lb/>Mitto itaque ad D. Herport affinem D. Stehelini literas in quibus dilucidatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes quaedam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ro, <del>at </del>sine quibus non facile esset pretium quod emere optarem
            <lb/>definire. Misit is mihi aliquot catalogi exempla, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cum amicis
            <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicarem <!-- hier fehlt ein Wort, RG 11.01.2024 --> in emendo operam perhumaniter obtulit. Nimirum
            <lb/>TIBI molestus forem si similia per TE agi vellem. De Telescopio Megar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>diano nil ne novi habes, cel. D. König Prof. HagCom. per Göttingam, Berolini
            <lb/>venit, is pluriora de ea re co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicare poterit. Specimina qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que
            <lb/>cathedra vacante physica prodeunt velim mecum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unices. Mea vicissim
            <lb/>opera in quacunque re TIBI fuerit utere. Bononienses edunt Ephemeri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>des Manfredi in 12 a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>os proximos continuatas. Priamus Jesuita Neapol.
            <lb/>cursum astronomi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> lingua Italica in folio conscripsit in quo se parum
            <lb/>recentiorum <add>Mathematicorum</add> cultorem exhibet. Donati primum Tomum histori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> naturalis <pb facs="3713807" n="3"/>
            <lb/>maris Adriatici edidit Venet. 1750 4<hi rend="sup">to</hi>. Musei regii Gallici descriptionem accepi
            <lb/>ex altera editione a<hi rend="sup">i</hi>. 1750 quam ad quaten<!-- diese beiden Wörter sind unklar, RG 11.01.2024 --> priori esse auctiorem. Prodiit quoq<choice><orig><g ref="#ue">uͤ</g></orig><reg>ü</reg></choice>
            <lb/><del/>a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o 1745 acad. regi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Scientiarum &amp; universum opus denuo sub
            <lb/>scriptionis lege imprimit in 78 voluminibus in 4<hi rend="sup">to</hi> <del>pro</del> 660 libris gallicis.
            <lb/>Nova alia non habeo.</p>
        <p><lb/>Vale cum nobiliss. conjuge &amp; splendida familia meq<choice><orig><g ref="#ue">uͤ</g></orig><reg>ü</reg></choice> perge amare.
            <lb/>Tiguri d. 17. oct. 1750</p><pb facs="3713808" n="4"/>
</div>
